{"tid":1425242,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"攰呀 但係都要企出黎","createTime":"2019-08-06T17:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T14:07:40.000Z","uid":3144,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"95909ba7621fdac25a2310cfaedf7607d7a31f1a","tid":1425242,"uid":3144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:31:54.000Z","msg":"好多人 包括我自己 都會覺得一個禮拜搞3,4日會有啲密 好想休息<br />\n但係當我係屋企睇到香港軍閥開始製造白色恐怖 濫捕各區街坊 恐嚇未被定罪嘅人時 我發現<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無力感同內疚仲辛苦過身體同精神嘅疲憊</span><br />\n當有人可以為咗自己嘅社區 自己嘅家 義無反顧咁抗衡各種嘅不公義 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我冇藉口再話要抖抖</span><br />\n我今日早前先同個friend講我地唔係機械人 我地都要休息下 <br />\n睇完深水埗啲咁撚柒on9嘅嘢之後 我會推翻昨日的我<br />\n希望大家唔好因為攰而放棄出席任何一個集會示威嘅機會<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">可以失望 但絕不能絕望</span><br />\n攰可以抖 但係一定要出返黎<br />\n行動派 和理非 缺一不可<br />\n而我會繼續盡量出席任何一場活動 做好我哨兵嘅工作<br />\n不受傷 不被補 不流血 祝武運亨通<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"a100f013c8354cf2f0e48b9fc9df2ea9cbcf54a4","tid":1425242,"uid":3144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:34:02.000Z","msg":"8.9-8.11 機場繼續和你飛<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ouTxJ7D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FouTxJ7D.jpg&h=3daf6430&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d447d2ecdd8c607bf288d7fafb37f4b6a721e2a","tid":1425242,"uid":3144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:39:17.000Z","msg":"8.11 深水埗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sBOmCun.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsBOmCun.jpg&h=cd0e7da8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26514c8e842bb3c52c24a6111c78a9e029126fa4","tid":1425242,"uid":3144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:40:41.000Z","msg":"8.11 港島東遊行<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gyZQvPE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgyZQvPE.jpg&h=06cb2ff4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da6eeec69f43c9bcf1fe946809e9f4b6cb3d3182","tid":1425242,"uid":3144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:42:43.000Z","msg":"8.10大埔遊行<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rj1SKax.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frj1SKax.jpg&h=56345d93&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"058b6ba26822269753da4ed342115e6ff889d0bd","tid":1425242,"uid":39568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:45:07.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n8月6日深水埗無差別拘捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1425299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1425299</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"09731c4a9752395da25c28c5c6cfdc042fafa9ff","tid":1425242,"uid":3144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:46:47.000Z","msg":"要記得我地嘅政權為市民做過啲乜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d95zXwT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd95zXwT.jpg&h=3f498dd2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1fa8ec2a7fedc05609e62688941ddd90df52afd9","tid":1425242,"uid":190727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:07:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7ed227035f20f4fc3c139d0f18652b666ac4b793","tid":1425242,"uid":190727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:07:40.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}